{"title":"地球绝唱","authors":["曹治淮"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":4,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"地球绝唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曹治淮诗　张耀宁画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的前景并不美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身上下尽是嘴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五十亿人在笑我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为粮食锁愁眉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人山人海把我围，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人满为患该怪谁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人口膨胀大爆炸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住房就业将生悲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人多耕地年年毁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的容颜变憔悴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生态平衡遭破坏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"环境恶化难挽回。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我已被人压弯腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也为人累细腿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们算计我血汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"负担超重太疲惫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劝人清醒别沉睡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温饱之时定思危，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果人口不控制，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们与我同倒霉！（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}